{"tid":409702,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"不屑子想帶兩老去泰國玩 求指點","createTime":"2017-09-22T09:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T10:00:26.000Z","uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"849f3d049d83c86071e8a1167e937d0f3aee5c8e","tid":409702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"黎緊十月 or 十一月想帶兩老去泰國旅行 <br />\n<br />\n大概去 4日3夜到<br />\n<br />\n因為睇到好多人都話泰國好正 人又nice 住同食都平靚正 好抵玩咁<br />\n<br />\n但小弟又未去過 對泰國無咩概念 <br />\n<br />\n例如：曼谷、 巴提雅、 清邁。⋯⋯ 各有咩特色分別 ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過下 但好多好似都係有關夜生活 同兩老一齊有d尷介<br />\n<br />\n所以想大家比少少行程意見<br />\n<br />\n有無咩活動景點係適合一家人 老少咸宜 等我有個方向 唔該大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c94dbd3cfb7f364a8a6145917a2192ef6f7130d","tid":409702,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"帶兩老去華欣嘆下"},{"pid":"f8dbe13e16a95c3c154a1c8bb3830460fa986ef3","tid":409702,"uid":121746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"帶老豆去叫雞"},{"pid":"52a3de4e0e216118446df76645843a41a9b88b9a","tid":409702,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"咩叫不屑子"},{"pid":"4c725f5622c0c8264fdc937d1baef8a9f309d3c1","tid":409702,"uid":20559,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫不屑子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不肖子不屑帶父母旅行"},{"pid":"621128d877b5f79072210877cbdea355ca4b1693","tid":409702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶老豆去叫雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次得我同佢會試下"},{"pid":"d0388969dbc624afc44fb1dea7e6ddbf67d036b4","tid":409702,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"帶阿媽試鴨仔"},{"pid":"1de8ec3fcf5a787886f3a14da914450e7aa0d486","tid":409702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶兩老去華欣嘆下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真 我查下華欣先 好似比較少聽"},{"pid":"9691ca2511a234e27516097fdf24ac4ce8df3ef0","tid":409702,"uid":52146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:52:42.000Z","msg":"掉幾千比旅行社咩都搞掂晒啦<br />\n自己唔駛一齊去"},{"pid":"81be0a7b82219f0df127a5d752541d71acb4ed2d","tid":409702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫不屑子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為老豆做野好辛苦 我又唔生性 所以想帶佢地出去一次旅行坐下飛機 （佢地未出過國）"},{"pid":"c66fcaab07eceb7781f47f22de92773d0f91af30","tid":409702,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"佢地都鐘意游水個啲水上活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739398deb3f0cc88f4852052c2143f260f3a3cf1","tid":409702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶阿媽試鴨仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢接受到就好"},{"pid":"30191ab17d2de6bbf0b9189a6712be6324af956a","tid":409702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>掉幾千比旅行社咩都搞掂晒啦<br />\n自己唔駛一齊去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我都覺自己仆街 老實講 我都唔想同屋企人去 唔係唔愛佢地 只係自己鐘意玩概同兩老唔同 所以今次主要係陪伴性質 佢地係主角 最緊要佢地開心"},{"pid":"10970eb685bfc5d8c395f445868a80dd12695248","tid":409702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地都鐘意游水個啲水上活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n  <br />\n老母同我都唔識游水 但如果你話坐香蕉船or激流都ok"}]}